n.k0s(),n.j41(21,"li"),n.EFF(22,"You agree not to use our Services in breach of any policy or other notice on our website."),n.k0s(),n.j41(23,"li"),n.EFF(24,"You agree not to remove or alter any copyright notices that appear on our website."),n.k0s(),n.j41(25,"li"),n.EFF(26,"You agree not to publish any material that may encourage a breach of any relevant laws or regulations."),n.k0s(),n.j41(27,"li"),n.EFF(28,"You agree not to misrepresent any information you submit for use on our website."),n.k0s(),n.j41(29,"li"),n.EFF(30,"You agree not to interfere with any other user's enjoyment of our website or the Services."),n.k0s(),n.j41(31,"li"),n.EFF(32,"You agree not to transmit materials protected by copyright without the permission of the owner."),n.k0s(),n.j41(33,"li"),n.EFF(34,"You agree not to conduct yourself in an offensive or abusive manner whilst using our website or the Services."),n.k0s()()(),n.j41(35,"section")(36,"h2",3),n.EFF(37,"Registration and security"),n.k0s(),n.j41(38,"p"),n.EFF(39,"You must be over eighteen years of age to register on our website and must ensure that the details provided by you on registration are true, accurate, current and complete. It is your responsibility to update and inform us of any changes to the details provided on registration. Although certain parts of our website may be used by anyone who visits without requiring registration, some of the Services require you to register in order to enable us to verify your identity."),n.k0s(),n.j41(40,"p"),n.EFF(41,"By registering with this service you give us permission to use your provided information for communication purposes about Homes services and occasional third party offers. You can unsubscribe from our communications at any time via the \u2018unsubscribe\u2019 link at the bottom of every communication we send out to users."),n.k0s(),n.j41(42,"p"),n.EFF(43,"When registering, you will be asked to create a password and will be responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of yo